{
  "stem": "9503.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I mean, I-- I-- I-- I can't fathom that, you know, for people who [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] did all the things one normally does and then not to have an opportunity.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I take a shower every day now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, it must have been very unpleasant.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I don't remember that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I don't have a sense of smell now at all, which is odd.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] The [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] camp-- toward the end, before liberation, the other camps were-- they sent, again, carloads of-- of prisoners from other camps to Theresienstadt in an attempt, I think, at the time, to escape that these camps were liberated.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And so we-- we got these cattle cars now coming back.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I remember that my mother volunteered, after hours, to help unload, because I'm sure she was looking for my father.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I remember standing in a-- in a line, you know, like, around the road where-- where people who came off the trains, and just going after my work and just standing there and watching what came by.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] a lot of them came by who couldn't walk, and they were dead.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And my mother never knew this, that I did this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But I wanted to see my father too, and he didn't show up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] with the people from the other camps came a typhus epidemic.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And so they started putting the people who came in from these transports in separate barracks.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They isolated a section of the camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then as my-- with my privilege of my card of being a messenger, I got into these-- into these barracks.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
